ph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559350/extras/139f14f96c270f27c90764addbb1aaf6.avif?t=1770666685\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559350/extras_big/139f14f96c270f27c90764addbb1aaf6.webp?t=1770666685 width=1560 height=858 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE LAYERS OF LIMBO</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the secret tombs of the Ossuary to the soaring spires of the Aviary, each layer of Limbo presents <strong>unique puzzles</strong> and <strong>hidden lore</strong> for those brave enough to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559350/extras/634136d58fc09c18ae748f0dae14dc94.avif?t=1770666685\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559350/extras_big/634136d58fc09c18ae748f0dae14dc94.webp?t=1770666685 width=1560 height=684 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Known as the graveyard of Limbo, the Ossuary is where beings traditionally lay their loved ones to rest. Tombs and gravestones sprawl across its surface, tended by locals who maintain the burial grounds. Beneath the earth lies a vast network of tombs, holding countless bodies and the buried secrets of their pasts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559350/extras/62226fbf7c663bb1fb57e98d6b5e1d5c.avif?t=1770666685\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559350/extras_big/62226fbf7c663bb1fb57e98d6b5e1d5c.webp?t=1770666685 width=1560 height=684 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Foundry stretches for hundreds of miles, dominated by a massive factory built over a sea of molten lava. Within its walls, locals toil day and night, tending machinery and producing much of Limbo's industrial goods. At the core of the factory beats the Machine Heart, driving production and enforcing the relentless rhythm of the layer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559350/extras/4222250d5de89fc2906800e4c47faae3.avif?t=1770666685\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559350/extras_big/4222250d5de89fc2906800e4c47faae3.webp?t=1770666685 width=1560 height=684 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Colliery sits at the base of a towering mountain, home to Limbo's largest repository of coal. Wooden buildings line the town's streets, leading to mines carved into the mountain's rocky base, where hidden secrets and monsters await further within.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559350/extras/7a1e8f1e505bd80b641fb0d9eff74cb9.avif?t=1770666685\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559350/extras_big/7a1e8f1e505bd80b641fb0d9eff74cb9.webp?t=1770666685 width=1560 height=684 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Sanctuary is a realm of beauty and reverence, graced by houses of worship and tranquil gardens. Its inhabitants faithfully uphold the rituals and traditions of the past, often without understanding their original meaning, as the truth that once defined them was buried long ago.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559350/extras/f1e08a6012722efc3576a4daf00fedc5.avif?t=1770666685\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559350/extras_big/f1e08a6012722efc3576a4daf00fedc5.webp?t=1770666685 width=1560 height=684 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Estuary is a swampland divided by a great river that cuts through the region, emptying into a vast body of water at the edge of Limbo. Along its banks, two rival tribes remain locked in conflict, each believing the other must answer for sins of the past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559350/extras/e048512280d9edfafceb8c7851275b49.avif?t=1770666685\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559350/extras_big/e048512280d9edfafceb8c7851275b49.webp?t=1770666685 width=1560 height=684 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crowned with towering spires and lavish architecture, the Aviary floats atop the clouds. It is home to Limbo's wealthy elite, whose appearance resembles the birds of our world. Though they possess everything they could desire, it is never enough to satisfy their craving for more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Reality calls you home. Will you return to her?</strong></p>",
